    \includegraphics[width=0.80 \columnwidth]{Fig1.eps}
    \caption{\label{Cs}The caesium D$_{2}$ line and the frequency splitting between the hyperfine components of the $6^{2}S_{1/2}$ ground and $6^{2}P_{3/2}$ excited states (not to scale). The transitions driven by the various laser fields, present in our LVIS trap, are shown as well.

}
